 A. Functional Requirement Questions (Must ask)
1. User & Roles

How many users?
What departments? (Purchase, Inventory, Production, Finance, QA, etc.)
What roles and permissions are needed?
Any approval hierarchy? (e.g., Purchase order ‚Üí Manager approval)

2. Plant Structure

Number of plants
Different warehouses?
Any inter‚Äëplant transfer rules?

3. Item & BOM Rules

Multi-level BOM or single level?
BOM revisions allowed?
Need routing and operations?
Costing method (FIFO, LIFO, Weighted Average)?

4. Purchase

PO approval workflows?
Vendor rating system?
GRN tolerances (% difference allowed)?

5. Inventory

Batch no. rules?
Expiry control required?
Do they use barcodes or QR codes?

6. Sales & Production

Need MRP?
Work orders auto-generated or manual?
Do they have machine capacity data?

7. QMS / CAPA / NCR / BD

Are they following ISO 9001, GMP, FDA, ISO 14001?
What QMS forms/templates they currently fill manually?
Required workflows and approval chains?

8. OEE

List of machines
PLC/SCADA access available?
Do they give real-time signals?
Do machines support OPC-UA or need IoT gateway?

9. Finance

Chart of accounts format?
Do they need Tally/SAP integration?
Financial year structure?

10. AI

What predictions do they expect?
Do they have past quality data, production logs, machine data?
Are AI recommendations auto or suggestion-based?


